<header>
<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="name"><a href="/news/nwavguy-o2-l-amplificateur-casque-sous-licence-creative-common">NwAvGuy O2 : l’amplificateur casque sous licence Creative Common</a></h1>
<div class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/rabbithood" rel="author">rabbithood</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-12-18T23:19:19+01:00"><span class="date">le 18/12/13</span> <span class="time">à 23:19</span></time>. Édité par <span class="edited_by"><a href="/users/davy78">Davy Defaud</a>, <a href="/users/jcr83">jcr83</a>, <a href="/users/baud123">baud123</a>, <a href="/users/oumph">Benoît Sibaud</a>, <a href="/users/beno%C3%AEt--3">Benoît</a>, <a href="/users/mrlapinot">MrLapinot</a>, <a href="/users/skc">Sébastien Koechlin</a>, <a href="/users/claudex">Xavier Claude</a>, <a href="/users/nyco">Nÿco</a>, <a href="/users/neox">NeoX</a> et <a href="/users/thenastyboy">Nils Ratusznik</a></span>. Modéré par <a href="/users/andrianarivony">ZeroHeure</a>.
<a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.fr" rel="license">Licence CC by-sa</a>
<div class="tags">
Tags :
<ul class="tag_cloud" itemprop="keywords">
<li><a href="/tags/audio/public" rel="tag">audio</a></li>
