<a class="title" href="/nodes/95280/comments/1508475">Re: au sujet du Vinyle vs CD vs MP3</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/kerro" rel="author">Kerro</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-12-19T20:33:49+01:00"><span class="date">le 19/12/13</span> <span class="time">à 20:33</span></time>.
