<h2>
<a class="parent" href="/news/nwavguy-o2-l-amplificateur-casque-sous-licence-creative-common#comment-1508256" title="Aller au commentaire parent">[^]</a>
<a class="anchor" href="/news/nwavguy-o2-l-amplificateur-casque-sous-licence-creative-common#comment-1508478" title="Lien direct vers ce commentaire">#</a>
 
<a class="title" href="/nodes/95280/comments/1508478">Re: canard</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/kerro" rel="author">Kerro</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-12-19T20:38:24+01:00"><span class="date">le 19/12/13</span> <span class="time">à 20:38</span></time>.
Évalué à&nbsp;<span class="score">
