<a class="title" href="/nodes/95280/comments/1509790">Re: CC BY-ND 3.0 (suite)</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/jgo" rel="author">JGO</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-12-28T18:55:19+01:00"><span class="date">le 28/12/13</span> <span class="time">à 18:55</span></time>.
